{"tid":1698903,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"我隻老婆婆倉鼠(小露寶)終於肯上我手食嘢！","createTime":"2019-11-07T23:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T10:52:59.000Z","uid":277072,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3e285b726f80b20d78726931d045c1783656306e","tid":1698903,"uid":277072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T23:38:29.000Z","msg":"最近患左抑鬱症 而家喺外國 成日掛住香港屋企隻狗<br />\n有一日去寵物店到睇動物見到依隻倉鼠係咁跑就好想帶佢番屋企<br />\n除左家姐十幾年前養過倉鼠之外對倉鼠係0認識<br />\n帶左佢番屋企做資料搜集先發現佢係最難上手嘅倉鼠<br />\n因為佢好細膽同跑得好快 已經有心理準備一世都抱唔到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我一直試 日日俾佢下隻手 佢終於上嚟食野 我好開心呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z2gXLHj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ2gXLHj.png&h=846ab600&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b73e25a3e6540fe20f0b813015f49cf8191fdcf6","tid":1698903,"uid":277072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T23:39:14.000Z","msg":"俾佢*聞下隻手"},{"pid":"ba8a92d88337a0c5f9b3107bf4d91e734ef3ea5b","tid":1698903,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T23:54:04.000Z","msg":"幸福"},{"pid":"0924f9a6e0c4cfab570c646f79ef07638e4311af","tid":1698903,"uid":144522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c8c091c964ef8768e665adba6b5211fff3021e","tid":1698903,"uid":183104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T00:03:07.000Z","msg":"細細粒咁好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n恭喜樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5733d5ddad50fd8356bb4914b957d8b642dd84a0","tid":1698903,"uid":277072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba8a92d88337a0c5f9b3107bf4d91e734ef3ea5b","tid":1698903,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-0